title: Barstool Pick Em 2017 Week Two
description:
EL Pres has made it 1 week before bowing out of podcasting duties so Big Cat called his friend Stanford Steve to break down the big games of the week as well as a call from our old friend Rico Bosco!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
